
## Video Specifications

### Promotional Videos
- Format: MP4 (H.264)
- Resolution: 1080p (1920x1080)
- Aspect Ratio: 16:9
- Max Duration: 2 minutes
- File naming: `promo-[title]-[date].mp4`

### Tutorial Videos
- Format: MP4 (H.264)
- Resolution: 720p (1280x720)
- Aspect Ratio: 16:9
- Max Duration: 10 minutes
- File naming: `tutorial-[topic]-[part].mp4`

### Testimonial Videos
- Format: MP4 (H.264)
- Resolution: 720p (1280x720)
- Aspect Ratio: 9:16 (vertical) or 16:9 (horizontal)
- Max Duration: 1 minute
- File naming: `testimonial-[name]-[date].mp4`

## Video Optimization

1. **Compression**: Use handbrake or ffmpeg for compression
2. **Thumbnails**: Generate thumbnail for each video
3. **Subtitles**: Include .srt files for accessibility
4. **Metadata**: Add appropriate metadata

## Recommended Tools

1. **FFmpeg** - Command line video processing
2. **HandBrake** - GUI video converter
3. **OBS Studio** - Screen recording
4. **DaVinci Resolve** - Video editing (free)

## Sample Video Placeholders

For development, you can use placeholder videos from:
- https://pixabay.com/videos/ (free stock videos)
- https://coverr.co/ (free stock videos)
- https://www.pexels.com/videos/ (free stock videos)

## Video Hosting Options

For production, consider:
1. **Self-hosted** - Serve directly from your server
2. **YouTube** - Embed YouTube videos
3. **Vimeo** - Professional video hosting
4. **Cloudflare Stream** - Paid streaming service

## Example Video Files

1. `promo-intro-2024.mp4` - Platform introduction
2. `tutorial-job-search-1.mp4` - Job search tutorial
3. `testimonial-john-2024.mp4` - User testimonial
4. `event-career-fair-2024.mp4` - Event recording
